overview.en: SCB is committed to creating a public chain platform to protect the rights and interests of consumers and drive car enterprises to continuously pursue excellence, so as to establish a high-quality Shared car display platform that millions of people can trust,promote the rapid spread of high-quality cars of high-quality enterprises, and let inferior cars have no place to hide.
overview.zh: 共享汽车链 SCB 致力于打造一个保障消费者权益、驱动车企不断逐优的公链平台，进而建立万众可信任的高品质共享汽车展示平台，促进优质企业的优质汽车被快速传播，让劣质汽车无处藏身。
